# $Header: $

  22 Feb 2008; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  By Hanno's request remove dependency to x11-drm git version.
  Someone may use this libdrm with in-kernel DRM.

  16 Feb 2008; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Patch from Peter Hjalmarsson (xake):
  Cleanups and properly build and install {dri,drm}stat.

  06 Nov 2007; Maarten Maathuis <madman2003@gmail.com> :
  Set EGIT_REPO_URI after inheriting the git eclass.

  16 Sep 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Add x11-drm as dep.

  08 May 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Remove -* from KEYWORDS.

  06 Apr 2007; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  Build dristat and drmstat, and install them. Some time in the past
  they were in x11-drm package, but that installs only kernel
  modules.

  21 Dec 2006; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  The nouveau-1 git branch for DRM has been merged to master branch.
  Switch to master branch.

*libdrm-9999 (30 Nov 2006)

  30 Nov 2006; Pekka Paalanen <pq@iki.fi> :
  I am picking up ebuild maintenance. Fixed git update issue.
